, Natalie</span>[[Natalie Portman]]\n| <span style=\"display:none\">Black Swan</span>''[[Black Swan (film)|Black Swan]]''\n| <span style=\"display:none\">1981-06-09</span>{{birth date|1981|6|9}}\n| {{Start date|2011|2|27}}\n| {{ayd|1981|6|9|2011|2|27}}\n| <span style=\"display:none\">{{CURRENTYEAR}}-{{CURRENTMONTH}}-{{CURRENTDAY}}</span>\n| ''{{formatnum:{{age in days|1981|6|9}}}}'' days ''({{ayd|1981|6|9}})''\n|\n|- style=\"text-align: left; background:#FFFFFF\"\n| 85\n| <span style=\"display:none\">Streep, Meryl</span>[[Meryl Streep]]\n| <span style=\"display:none\">Iron Lady</span>''[[The Iron Lady (film)|The Iron Lady]]''\n| <span style=\"display:none\">1949-06-22</span>{{birth date|1949|6|22}}\n| {{Start date|2012|2|26}}\n| {{ayd|1949|6|22|2012|2|26}}\n| <span style=\"display:none\">{{CURRENTYEAR}}-{{CURRENTMONTH}}-{{CURRENTDAY}}</span>\n| ''{{formatnum:{{age in days|1949|6|22}}}}'' days ''({{ayd|1949|6|22}})''\n| 2nd of 2\n|- style=\"text-align: left; background:#FFFFFF\"\n| 86\n| <span style=\"display:none\">Lawrence, Jennifer</span>[[Jennifer Lawrence]]\n| <span style=\"display:none\">Silver Linings Playbook</span>''[[Silver Linings Playbook]]''\n| <span style=\"display:none\">1990-08-15</span>{{birth date|1990|8|15}}\n| {{Start date|2013|2|24}}\n| {{ayd|1990|8|15|2013|2|24}}\n| <span style=\"display:none\">{{CURRENTYEAR}}-{{CURRENTMONTH}}-{{CURRENTDAY}}</span>\n| <span style=\"display:none\">''0{{formatnum:{{age in days|1990|8|15}}}}'' days ''({{ayd|1990|8|15}})'' </span>''{{formatnum:{{age in days|1990|8|15}}}}'' days ''({{ayd|1990|8|15}})''\n|\n|- style=\"text-align: left; background:#FFFFFF\"\n| 87\n|<span style=\"display:none\">Blanchett, Cate</span>[[Cate Blanchett]]\n|<span style=\"display:none\">Blue Jasmine</span>''[[Blue Jasmine]]''\n|<span style=\"display:none\">1969-05-14</span>{{birth date|1969|5|14}}\n| {{Start date|2014|3|2}}\n|{{ayd|1969|5|14|2014|3|2}}\n|<span style=\"display:none\">{{CURRENTYEAR}}-{{CURRENTMONTH}}-{{CURRENTDAY}}</span>\n| ''{{formatnum:{{age in days|1969|5|14}}}}'' days ''({{ayd|1969|5|14}})''\n|\n|- style=\"text-align: left; background:#FFFFFF\"\n| 88\n|<span style=\"display:none\">Moore, Julianne</span>[[Julianne Moore]]\n|<span style=\"display:none\">Still Alice</span>''[[Still Alice]]''\n|<span style=\"display:none\">1960-12-03</span>{{birth date|1960|12|3}}\n| {{Start date|2015|2|22}}\n|{{ayd|1960|12|3|2015|2|22}}\n|<span style=\"display:none\">{{CURRENTYEAR}}-{{CURRENTMONTH}}-{{CURRENTDAY}}</span>\n| ''{{formatnum:{{age in days|1960|12|3}}}}'' days ''({{ayd|1960|12|3}})''\n|\n|- style=\"text-align: left; background:#FFFFFF\"\n| 89\n|<span style=\"display:none\">Larson, Brie</span>[[Brie Larson]]\n|<span style=\"display:none\">Room</span>''[[Room (2015 film)|Room]]''\n|<span style=\"display:none\">1989-10-01</span>{{birth date|1989|10|1}}\n| {{Start date|2016|2|28}}\n|{{ayd|1989|10|1|2016|2|28}}\n|<span style=\"display:none\">{{CURRENTYEAR}}-{{CURRENTMONTH}}-{{CURRENTDAY}}</span>\n| ''{{formatnum:{{age in days|1989|10|1}}}}'' days ''({{ayd|1989|10|1}})''\n|\n|- style=\"text-align: left; background:#FFFFFF\"\n| 90\n|<span style=\"display:none\">Stone, Emma</span>[[Emma Stone]]\n|<span style=\"display:none\">La La Land</span>''[[La La Land (film)|La La Land]]''\n|<span style=\"display:none\">1988-11-06</span>{{birth date|1988|11|6}}\n| {{Start date|2017|2|26}}\n|{{ayd|1988|11|6|2017|2|26}}\n|<span style=\"display:none\">{{CURRENTYEAR}}-{{CURRENTMONTH}}-{{CURRENTDAY}}</span>\n| ''{{formatnum:{{age in days|1988|11|6}}}}'' days ''({{ayd|1988|11|6}})''\n|\n|- style=\"text-align: left; background:#FFFFFF\"\n| 91\n| <span style=\"display:none\">Mcdormand, Frances</span>[[Frances McDormand]]\n| <span style=\"display:none\">Three Billboards Outside Ebbing, Missouri</span>''[[Three Billboards Outside Ebbing, Missouri]]''\n| <span style=\"display:none\">1957-06-23</span>{{birth date|1957|6|23}}\n| {{Start date|2018|3|4}}\n| {{ayd|1957|6|23|2018|3|4}}\n| <span style=\"display:none\">{{CURRENT