=\"UCL\"/>||2||1<ref group=\"lower-alpha\" name=\"ITA\"/>||0||34||6\n|-\n||[[2004\u201305 Serie A|2004\u201305]]\n|27||7||1||0||10<ref group=\"lower-alpha\" name=\"UCL\"/>||3||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||47||7\n|-\n||[[2005\u201306 Serie A|2005\u201306]]\n|33||5||4||0||8<ref group=\"lower-alpha\" name=\"UCL\"/>||2||1<ref group=\"lower-alpha\" name=\"ITA\"/>||0||45||13\n|-\n||[[2006\u201307 Serie B|2006\u201307]]\n|[[Serie B]]\n|33||11||3||1||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||36||12\n|-\n||[[2007\u201308 Serie A|2007\u201308]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Serie A\n|31||2||2||1||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||33||3\n|-\n||[[2008\u201309 Serie A|2008\u201309]]\n|32||7||3||0||9<ref group=\"lower-alpha\" name=\"UCL\"/>||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||44||7\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!247!!51!!22!!5!!55!!12!!3!!0!!327!!65\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career total\n!501!!110!!44!!7!!118!!29!!6!!1!!669!!147\n|}\n{{Reflist|group=lower-alpha}}\n\n===International===\nSource: <ref name=NFTprofile/><ref name=\"rsssf\">{{cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/nedved-intl.html|title=Pavel Nedved \u2013 International Appearances|publisher=Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation|accessdate=4 March 2013}}</ref>\n{| class=wikitable style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|+ Appearances and goals by national team and year\n|-\n!National team!!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=\"13\"|[[Czech Republic national football team|Czech Republic]]\n|1994||1||0\n|-\n|1995||4||0\n|-\n|1996||12||2\n|-\n|1997||10||2\n|-\n|1998||3||1\n|-\n|1999||9||2\n|-\n|2000||10||4\n|-\n|2001||11||4\n|-\n|2002||6||0\n|-\n|2003||8||2\n|-\n|2004||9||0\n|-\n|2005||2||0\n|-\n|2006||6||1\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total!!91!!18\n|}\n\n==== International goals ====\n:''Scores and results list Czech Republic's goal tally first.<ref name=\"rsssf\"/>\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! # !! Date !! Venue !! Opponent !! Score !! Result !! Competition\n|-\n| 1 || 14 June 1996 || [[Anfield]], Liverpool || {{fb|ITA}} || 1\u20130 || 2\u20131 || [[UEFA Euro 1996|Euro 1996]]\n|-\n| 2 || 18 September 1996 || [[Na St\u00ednadlech]], Teplice || {{fb|MLT}} || 2\u20130 || 6\u20130 || [[1998 FIFA World Cup qualification|1998 World Cup qualification]]\n|-\n| 3 || rowspan=\"2\" | 17 December 1997 || rowspan=\"2\" | [[King Fahd II Stadium]], Riyadh || rowspan=\"2\" | {{fb|UAE}} || 2\u20130 || rowspan=\"2\" | 6\u20131 || rowspan=\"2\" | [[1997 FIFA Confederations Cup|1997 Confederations Cup]]\n|-\n| 4 || 3\u20130\n|-\n| 5 || 14 October 1998 || Na St\u00ednadlech, Teplice || {{fb|EST}} || 1\u20130 || 4\u20131 || [[UEFA Euro 2000 qualifying|Euro 2000 qualifying]]\n|-\n| 6 || rowspan=\"2\" | 4 September 1999 || rowspan=\"2\" | [[\u017dalgiris Stadium]], Vilnius || rowspan=\"2\" | {{fb|LTU}} || 1\u20130 || rowspan=\"2\" | 4\u20130 || rowspan=\"2\" | Euro 2000 qualifying\n|-\n| 7 || 2\u20130\n|-\n| 8 || rowspan=\"2\" | 26 March 2000 || rowspan=\"2\" | [[Generali Arena]], Prague || rowspan=\"2\" | {{fb|ISR}} || 1\u20130 || rowspan=\"2\" | 4\u20131 || rowspan=\"2\" | [[Exhibition game|Friendly]]\n|-\n| 9 || 3\u20130\n|-\n| 10 || rowspan=\"2\" | 7 October 2000 || rowspan=\"2\" | Na St\u00ednadlech, Teplice || rowspan=\"2\" | {{fb|ISL}} || 3\u20130 || rowspan=\"2\" | 4\u20130 || rowspan=\"2\" | [[2002 FIFA World Cup qualification|2002 World Cup qualification]]\n|-\n| 11 || 4\u20130\n|-\n| 12 || 24 March 2001 || [[Windsor Park]], [[Belfast]] || {{fb|NIR}} || 1\u20130 || 1\u20130 || 2002 World Cup qualification\n|-\n| 13 || 15 August 2001 || Sportovn\u00ed are\u00e1l, [[Drnovice (Vy\u0161kov District)|Drnovice]] || {{fb|KOR}} || 1\u20130 || 5\u20130 || Friendly\n|-\n| 14 || rowspan=\"2\" | 6 October 2001 || rowspan=\"2\" | Generali Arena, Prague || rowspan=\"2\" | {{fb|BUL}} || 2\u20130 || rowspan=\"2\" | 6\u20130 || rowspan=\"2\" | 2002 World Cup qualification\n|-\n| 15 || 6\u20130\n|-\n| 16 || 2 April 2003 || [[Generali Arena|Toyota Arena]], Prague || {{fb|AUT}} || 1\u20130 || 4\u20130 || [[UEFA Euro 2004 qualifying|Euro 2004 qualifying]]\n|-\n| 17 || 6 September 2003 || [[Dinamo Stadium (Minsk)|Dinamo Stadium]], Minsk || {{fb|BLR}} || 1\u20131 || 3\u20131 || Euro 2004 qualifying\n|-\n| 18 || 6 June 2006 || Toyota Arena, Prague || {{fb|TRI}} || 2\u20130 || 3\u20130 || Friendly\n|}\n\n== Honours ==\n[[File:Otisk nohy Pavla Nedv\u011bda v Monaku.jpg|thumb|alt=A golden cast of Nedved's footprints. His signature and the date are recorded at the top of the image.|Nedved's [[Golden Foot]].]]\n\n=== Club ===\n'''Sparta Prague'''<ref name=jerabek/>\n*[[Czechoslovak First League]]: [[1992\u201393 Czechoslovak First League|1992\u201393]]\n*[[Gambrinus liga|Czech Republic Football League]]: [[1993\u201394 Gambrinus liga|1993\u201394]], [[1994\u201395 Gambrinus liga|1994\u201395]]\n*[[Czech Cup]]: [[1995\u201396 Czech Cup|1996]]\n\n'''Lazio'''<ref name=Soccerway-profile>{{Soccerway|pavel-nedved/257}}. Retrieved 4 June 2013.</ref>\n*[[Serie A]]: [[1999\u20132000 Serie A|1999\u20132000]]\n*[[Coppa Italia]]: [[1997\u201398 Coppa Italia|1997\u201398]], [[1999\u20132000 Coppa Italia|1999\u20132000]]\n*[[Supercoppa Italiana]]: [[1998 Supercoppa Italiana|1998]], [[2000 Supercoppa Italiana|2000]]\n*[[UEFA Cup Winners' Cup]]: [[1998\u201399 UEFA Cup Winners' Cup|1998\u201399]]\n*[[UEFA Super Cup]]: [[1999 UEFA Super Cup|1999]]\n*[[UEFA Europa League|UEFA Cup]]: Runner-up [[1997\u201398 UEFA Cup|1997\u201398]]\n\n'''Juventus'''<ref name=Soccerway-profile/>\n*[[Serie A]]: [[2001\u201302 Serie A|2001\u201302]], [[2002\u201303 Serie A|2002\u201303]]\n*[[Supercoppa Italiana]]: [[2002 Supercoppa Italiana|2002]], [[2003 Supercoppa Italiana|2003]]\n*[[Serie B]]: [[2006\u201307 Serie B|2006\u201307]]\n*[[UEFA Champions League]]: Runner-up [[2002\u201303 UEFA Champions League|2002\u201303]]\n*[[Coppa Italia]]: Runner-up [[2001\u201302 Coppa Italia|2001\u201302]], [[2003\u201304 Coppa Italia|2003\u201304]]\n\n=== International ===\n'''Czech Republic'''\n*[[UEFA European Championship]]:\n**Runner-up: [[UEFA Euro 1996|1996]]<ref n