le's list of the greatest |publisher=BBC Sport |date=4 March 2004 |accessdate=15 June 2013 }}</ref>\n*[[FAI International Football Awards]] \u2013 International Personality: 2012<ref name=fai-awards/>\n*[[UEFA Team of the Year#UEFA Ultimate Team of the Year|UEFA Ultimate Team of the Year]] (substitute; published 2015)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/news/newsid=2201679.html|title=Ultimate Team of the Year: The All-Time XI|publisher=UEFA|date=22 November 2015|accessdate=25 November 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Juventus F.C.|Juventus Greatest XI of All Time]]: 2017<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.juventus.com/en/news/news/2017/juve120-team-announced.php|title=#JUVE120 team announced|publisher=juventus.com|date=24 November 2017|accessdate=29 May 2018}}</ref>\n\n== Bibliography ==\n*{{cite book |last=Nedv\u011bd |first=Pavel |title=La mia vita normale: di corsa tra rivoluzione, Europa, e pallone d'oro |trans-title= |language=Italian |location=Torino |year=2010 |publisher=ADD Editore |isbn=978-8896873090}}\n*{{cite book |last1=Nedv\u011bd |first1=Pavel |last2=Dalai |first2=Michele |title=M\u016fj oby\u010dejn\u00fd \u017eivot: b\u011bh od revoluce do Evropy a ke Zlat\u00e9mu m\u00ed\u010di |trans-title= |language=Czech |location=Prague |year=2011 |publisher=Argo |isbn=978-80-257-0401-1}}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{Commons category|Pavel Nedv\u011bd}}\n* {{Official website|http://www.pavelnedved.cz/}}\n* {{FACR player}}\n* {{cite web |url=http://www.juventus.com/site/eng/TAS_schedagiocatoreprimasquadra_AABB522BE0F142728637A83A4A2EE428.asp |title=Juventus profile|publisher=Juventus.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090305143500/http://juventus.com/site/eng/TAS_schedagiocatoreprimasquadra_AABB522BE0F142728637A83A4A2EE428.asp|archivedate=5 March 2009|accessdate=20 March 2012}}\n* {{cite web |url=http://www.footballdatabase.com/site/players/index.php?dumpPlayer=428|title=Career profile and stats|publisher=FootballDataba